channel.title: NaJ Powerfull House Podcast
channel.description:
** DJ NaJ ** house Music ** -
NaJ is one of the French djs.
His musical influence can be heard in the most populars artists of US references, Who appreciate warm and passionate Pumpin and Deep House.
Always respectful of a unique musical style, mixing House funky & deep music atmosphere.
NaJ spreading his sound in many events abroad. links >>> www.naj.fr - www.najcloud.com
